INSERT INTO `productdetails` VALUES (1,'Dogfood1.webp','Dogfood1_2.webp','Dogfood1_3.webp','Arden Grange Chicken & Rice Adult Large Breed Dog Dry Food',500.00,'High-quality, hypoallergenic, international dog food','dogfood','Besides easily digested chicken oil as a fat source, it also has the nutrients required to strengthen your dogs joints and cartilage'),(2,'Dogfood2.webp','Dogfood2_1.webp','Dogfood2_2.webp','Chappi Chicken & Milk Dry Puppy Food',700.00,'Easy to digest, low fat, balanced dog food','dogfood','100% Complete and balanced food for adult dogs\",\"Contains a special blend of low fat and dietary fibre\",\"Easily digestible for even the most sensitive dogs\",\n\"A good source of protein and polyunsaturated fatty acids'),(3,'Dogfood3.webp','Dogfood3_1.webp','Dogfood3_2.webp','Fabled Happy To Sea With Salmon, Tuna, White Fish & Cod Adult Dog Food',1000.00,'This is a non Veg Product','dogfood','#1 INGREDIENT IS DELICIOUS FRESH MEAT: Every kibble is packed with fresh chicken, turkey and duck\nHEALTHY OIL & GOOD FAT: Contains healthy oil and good fat and is tailored nutrition for a healthy heart, liver, gut, skin and brain'),(4,'Dogfood41.webp','Dogfood4_1.webp','Dogfood4_2.webp','Pedigree Adult Dry Dog Food- Chicken & Vegetables, 1Kg Pack',1000.00,'Complete pet food for adult dogs, Healthy vitality - with high quality meat proteins, No added sugar, \nNo artificial colours or flavours','dogfood','Pedigree Chicken and Vegetables Adult Dog Dry Food is crafted to provide your adult dog a balanced and nutritious diet. This premium dog food combines the goodness of real chicken with wholesome vegetables, \noffering a delicious and complete meal that caters to your dogs daily nutritional needs.'),(5,'Dogfood51.webp','Dogfood5_1.webp','Dogfood5_2.webp','Sniffy Chicken & Egg All Breed Puppy Food 3 kg',1400.00,'Promotes healthy bone and muscle growth for a strong and active pup','dogfood','Whole Chicken and Egg Formula: SNIFFY Premium Puppy Dry Dog Food is crafted with the goodness of real chicken and egg, providing your \nfurry friend with a high-quality protein source for optimal muscle development and overall health.'),(6,'Dogaccessories1.webp','Dogaccessories1_2.webp','Dogaccessories1_3.webp','Savic Trotter 2 Pet Carrier for Cats and Small Dogs weighing up to 7 kg, Dark Grey',3100.00,'Savic Trotter 2 Pet Carrier for Cats and Small Dogs (Dark Grey) \nis suitable for a single pet with a weight of 7 kg.','dogaccessories','Designed to suit IATA standards, the Savic Trotter 2 Pet Carrier is great way to keep your pet safe on a journey. It can be used for any type of travel including air travel. Air vents ensure there is enough air circulation as does the metal door. \nSuitable for one pet at a time.'),(7,'Dogaccessories2.webp','Dogaccessories2_1.webp','Dogaccessories2_2.webp','Petsnugs Bone and Paws Sweater For Dog and Cats (XS)',900.00,'Charming Design: Featuring a cute printed caricature of Bones and Paws,\n this sweater adds a touch of charm and personality to your pets attire.','dogaccessories','Knitted. Soft, Stretchable & Lightweight. High Tummy Cut for Male Doggies to Relieve Themselves with Ease. Easy To Move In.\nWe Recommend Pet Parental Supervision when pets are wearing clothes. Please remove when your pet is exercising or playing.\nOuter : 100% Acrylic. Inner: Polyester\nSleeves: Sleeveless; Pattern: Solid; \nWeave: Knit; Closure: Elastic\nApplicable for all life stages for Dogs & Cats'),(8,'Dogaccessories3.webp','Dogaccessorie3_1.webp','Dogaccessorie3_2.webp','Printed Harness with Leash for Small Size Dogs (Multi Colors))',1100.00,'Durable and Soft: Constructed from high-quality nylon, the harness is both durable and soft, ensuring your pets\n comfort during walks and outings.','dogaccessories','Size - please refer to the size chart image for correct item dimensions. Easy On Easy Off Design Makes Putting It on Your Dog Hassle Free\nPulling Pressure is Evenly Distributed to the Body to Prevent Pulling and Choking\n2 Sturdy Metal Leash Attachment Points on the Back and on the Chest\nAdjustable Slide Straps Let You Create a Custom Fit for Your Dog\nReflective Straps ensure Your Dog’s Safety while out for a Walk Soft Breathable Material plus Heavy Padding Makes Your Dog Enjoys Wearing It'),(9,'Dogaccessories4.jpg','Dogaccessories4_1.jpg','Dogaccessories4_2.webp','ZEE.DOG Zee Bed for Dogs',9000.00,'Antimicrobial, 100% Memory foam (viscoelastic unibody foam core) dog bed with orthpedic support','dogaccessories','Your dog spends 80% of their lifetime sleeping. The Zee.Bed was designed to be the world’s most comfortable dog bed. Make a good choice.\n\nKey Features:\n\nUltra comfortable memory foam orthopedic dog bed – perfect for all dogs!\nSoft, removable, microfiber, hypoallergenic bed cover that’s easy to clean\nThe orthopedic dog beds removable cover has two zippers for easy removal\nAnti-slip rubber bottom – ensures the bed remains in one spot\nCushioned head support for maximum comfort\nPacked using nano-compression technology\nNo assembly required. Unbox and sleep\nSize Guide:\n\nLength\n\nSmall 24.8 in\nLarge 31.9 in\nWidth'),(10,'Dogaccessories5.webp','Dogaccessories5_1.webp','Dogaccessories5_2.webp','Petkin Bac-Stuffed Dentalbone (Medium/Large)',700.00,'Small brush like ridges develop in the bone as your dog \nchews that work like a toothbrush to clean teeth and remove soft plaque.','dogaccessories','Bac-Stuffed DentalBone provides an easy way to keep your dog’s teeth and gums healthy with a bone they’ll love to chew! This strong long lasting nylon bone has bacon flavor stuffed right in the middle to entertain \nyour dog’s natural chewing, smelling and tasting instincts and encourage hours of chewing satisfaction.Small brush like ridges develop in the bone as \nyour dog chews that work like a toothbrush to clean teeth and remove soft plaque\nTough, durable nylon is doggie-safe and built strong to chew long with a satisfying texture.\nBacon flavor in the middle keeps dogs engaged to chew longer\nHelps to promote dental stimulation, which is good for oral health.'),(11,'Doggrooming1.webp','Doggrooming1_2.webp','Doggrooming1_3.webp','Wahl Four in One Lavender Chamomile Shampoo for Dogs',850.00,'Cleans, conditions, detangles and moisturizes.Natural plant derived.\nWahl shampoo is peg-80 free','doggrooming','Introducing a Gentle Natural, Hypoallergenic Anti Hairfall Shampoo, designed to provide a mild and soothing experience for pets of all breeds, including dogs, cats, and pups.\n\nKey Features:\n\nAll-Natural and Safe: A gentle formula that cleans and conditions the hair, effectively reducing hair fall and excess shedding.\nFull Body Deep Cleansing: Promotes a thorough cleanse for the entire body, fostering healthy skin and a lustrous coat.\nMild Fragrance: Enjoy a subtle fragrance that restores softness and bounce to your pets fur.\nGentle Hypoallergenic Formula: Specially formulated with a hypoallergenic blend, free from SLES, Parabens, and Sulphates, ensuring a mild and safe experience for your pet.'),(12,'Doggrooming2.webp','Doggrooming2_1.jpeg','Doggrooming2_2.jpeg','AFP Sparkles Toothpaste Peanut Butter Flavor For Dogs',455.00,'Natural ingredients for advanced breath freshening and teeth whitening','doggrooming','All For Paws AFP Sparkle toothpastes for dogs are formulated with baking soda to disolve particles deep in the microscopic crevices on the tooth surface for maximum strength cleaning.\nIt is also formulated with natural ingredients for advanced breath freshening and teeth whitening.\n• 2.1 oz\n• Formulated with baking soda to dissolve particles and freshen breath\n• Features natural ingredients for advanced breath freshening and teeth whitening\n• Peanut Butter Flavour'),(13,'Doggrooming3.webp','Doggrooming3_1.webp','Doggrooming3_2.webp','E-Cloth Pet Grooming Mitt',1850.00,'Designed with a comfortable and adjustable strap, ensuring a secure fit on your \nhand during grooming sessions.','doggrooming','It is a versatile and effective tool for grooming pets.\nIdeal for use between baths to keep your pets coat fresh and odor-free.\nMade from high-quality microfiber material, it provides a gentle and thorough grooming experience.\nRemoves loose pet hair, dirt, and dander.\nDesigned with a comfortable and adjustable strap, ensuring a secure fit on your hand during grooming sessions.\nEasy to clean and maintain; simply rinse it with water and hang it to dry.\nPromotes a healthier coat by distributing natural oils and improving blood circulation.\nReduces shedding and minimizes allergies caused by pet hair.'),(14,'Doggrooming4.webp','Doggrooming4_1.webp','Doggrooming4_2.webp','Captain Zack Scent’sationally Yours Cologne Spray – Apple & Green Tea 100 ml',350.00,'Daily Use Natural Pet Perfume Spray','doggrooming','alcohol free fragrance for pets Spritz your pet with the soothing and fresh blend of Apple & Green Tea. The Captain Zack Scent’sationally Yours Cologne Spray will make your pets smell as great as they look. Infused with Apple and Green Tea Extracts, it is nourishing and instantly helps control odour.\nBetter yet, it is really gentle and alcohol-free to prevent skin irritation. Simply spray it on and your pet is ready to be super social!'),(15,'Doggrooming5.webp','Doggrooming5_1.webp','Doggrooming5_2.webp','LetsShave EZ-WIZZY Pet Trimmer for Dogs',2999.00,'Waterproof trimmer Powerful Lithium Battery- 1200 mAh\nLong Lasting Battery- 120 mins runtime in 120 mins of charging','doggrooming','The EZ-Wizzy Pet Trimmer from LetsShave is a top-grade trimmer that helps in grooming your dogs and cats effectively. This trimmer has a silent operation that keeps your pets at ease while removing their hairs, which also assists you to clean them without any hassles. The EZ-Wizzy Pet Trimmer suits almost all types of fur such as thick, silky, matty, thin, smooth, short, wavy, curly etc. The ceramic blade glides on your pet’s skin smoothly and gently, and allows you to groom them in laser precision. Bes