ilitates growth of blood cells.\nThese Biskies make the teeth & bones of your beloved pup stronger\nThese freshly baked biskies are an ideal training treat.'),(19,'catfood1.webp','catfood1_1.webp','catfood1_2.webp','Farmina Matisse Kitten Cat Food 10 Kg',1650.00,'Consists of Delicious Chicken & Rice: Apart from being yummy, it\n also bolsters the overall health of the kittens','catfood','This premium feline food from Matisse features salmon and tuna as their main ingredients. It is rich in taurine (an essential nutrient for cats) and is highly digestible. The Matisse Premium Dry Cat Food is a complete food for cats.\nFeatures:\nRich in taurine\nHighly digestible\nCruelty Free research\nAlways have fresh water available for your pet'),(20,'catfood2.webp','catfood2_1.webp','catfood2_2.webp','Whiskas Wet Cat Food for Adult Cats (1+Years), Tuna in Jelly Flavour, 14 Pouches (14 x 80g)',595.00,'Builds a Robust Immunity: Essential vitamins and minerals \nfor boosting metabolism as well as immunity','catfood','Introducing something new and tasty that is made using varieties of ingredients with complete & balanced nutrition and flavours that your furry friend will love. The new Whiskas Pouch Tasty Mix enhances the cat food’s\n deliciousness by combining quality protein with chicken and nutrition from colourful veggies in tasty gravy sauce. A cats love for fish is thoughtfully blended in Whiskas cat food along with 41 essential nutrients to boost their health & energy. \nThis is an ideal gravy food for cats that will make them happy while they also enjoy it.\n\nKey Features:\n\nMADE WITH REAL FISH: Whiskas Tasty Mix contains real fish which is easy to eat, ideal to be given to cat\nNEW POUCHES: Offers varieties in all the favourite protein flavours that your cat will love\nTEMPTING FLAVOUR: Cat Food made with Chicken and veggies like Salmon Wakame Seaweed in gravy to attract fussy eaters '),(21,'catfood3.webp','catfood3_1.webp','catfood3_2.webp','Me-O Delite Tuna Mousse with 